> **覆盖的类/函数**：`children`, `named_children`, `modules`, `named_modules`, `get_submodule`  
> **PyTorch 源码**：[torch/nn/modules/module.py](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/main/torch/nn/modules/module.py)  
